{"parents": [], "prev": {"link": "../../rh_primitives/table/", "title": "Table"}, "next": {"link": "../../overview/overview/", "title": "High Level Overview"}, "title": "Secrets Management", "meta": {}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"secrets-management\">\n<h1>Secrets Management<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#secrets-management\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Runhouse provides a convenient interface for managing your secrets in a secure manner.\nSecrets are stored in <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://www.vaultproject.io/\">Vault</a>, and never on Runhouse servers.</p>\n<div class=\"admonition tip\">\n<p class=\"admonition-title\">Tip</p>\n<p>See <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../overview/secrets/#vault-secrets\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">Vault Secrets</span></a> for more details on using the Secrets API.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"secrets\">\n<h2>secrets<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#secrets\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<dl class=\"py class\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">class</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-prename descclassname\"><span class=\"pre\">runhouse.</span></span><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">Secrets</span></span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Handles cluster secrets management (reading and writing) across all major cloud providers.\nSecrets are stored in Vault.\nChecks for locally configured secrets before pulling down or saving to Vault.</p>\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.delete\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">delete</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">providers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">List</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.delete\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.delete\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Delete secrets from Vault for the specified providers.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.download_into_env\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">download_into_env</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">save_locally</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">bool</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">providers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">List</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">headers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">&#x2192;</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">Dict</span></span></span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.download_into_env\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.download_into_env\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Get all user secrets from Vault. Optionally save them down to local config files (where relevant).</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.enabled_providers\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">enabled_providers</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">as_str</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">bool</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">&#x2192;</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">List</span></span></span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.enabled_providers\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.enabled_providers\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Returns a list of cloud provider class objects which have been enabled locally. If as_str is True,\nreturn the names of the providers as strings.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.extract_and_upload\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">extract_and_upload</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">headers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">interactive</span></span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">True</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">providers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">List</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.extract_and_upload\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.extract_and_upload\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Upload all locally configured secrets into Vault. Secrets are loaded from their local config files.\n(ex: ~/.aws/credentials). We currently support AWS, Azure, and GCP. To upload custom secrets for\nadditional providers, see <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.put\" title=\"runhouse.Secrets.put\"><code class=\"xref py py-func docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">put()</span></code></a>.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.get\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">get</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">provider</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">str</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">save_to_env</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">bool</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">group</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">&#x2192;</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">dict</span></span></span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.get\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.get\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Read secrets from the Vault service for a given provider and optionally save them to their local config.\nIf group is provided will read secrets for the specified group.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.load_provider_secrets\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">load_provider_secrets</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">from_env</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">bool</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">providers</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">List</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span> <span class=\"sig-return\"><span class=\"sig-return-icon\">&#x2192;</span> <span class=\"sig-return-typehint\"><span class=\"pre\">List</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">Dict</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">,</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span></span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.load_provider_secrets\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.load_provider_secrets\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Load secret credentials for all the providers which have been configured locally, or optionally\nprovide a list of specific providers to load</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.put\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">put</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">provider</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">str</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">from_env</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">bool</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">False</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">file_path</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">secret</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">dict</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em>, <em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">group</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">Optional</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">[</span></span><span class=\"pre\">str</span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">]</span></span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\"><span class=\"pre\">=</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"default_value\"><span class=\"pre\">None</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.put\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.put\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Upload locally configured secrets for a specified provider into Vault.</p>\n<p>To upload secrets for a custom provider (i.e. not AWS, GCP or Azure), include the secret param and specify\nthe keys and values to upload.</p>\n<p>If from_env is True, will read secrets from environment variables instead of local config files.\nIf file_path is provided, will read the secrets directly from the file\nIf group is provided, will attribute the secrets to the specified group</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n<dl class=\"py method\">\n<dt class=\"sig sig-object py\" id=\"runhouse.Secrets.save_provider_secrets\">\n<em class=\"property\"><span class=\"pre\">classmethod</span><span class=\"w\"> </span></em><span class=\"sig-name descname\"><span class=\"pre\">save_provider_secrets</span></span><span class=\"sig-paren\">(</span><em class=\"sig-param\"><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">secrets</span></span><span class=\"p\"><span class=\"pre\">:</span></span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\"><span class=\"pre\">dict</span></span></em><span class=\"sig-paren\">)</span><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../_modules/runhouse/rns/secrets/#Secrets.save_provider_secrets\"><span class=\"viewcode-link\"><span class=\"pre\">[source]</span></span></a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#runhouse.Secrets.save_provider_secrets\" title=\"Permalink to this definition\">\u00b6</a></dt>\n<dd><p>Save secrets for each provider to their respective local configs.</p>\n</dd></dl>\n\n</dd></dl>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n    <script type=\"text/x-thebe-config\">\n    {\n        requestKernel: true,\n        binderOptions: {\n            repo: \"binder-examples/jupyter-stacks-datascience\",\n            ref: \"master\",\n        },\n        codeMirrorConfig: {\n            theme: \"abcdef\",\n            mode: \"python\"\n        },\n        kernelOptions: {\n            kernelName: \"python3\",\n            path: \"./secrets\"\n        },\n        predefinedOutput: true\n    }\n    </script>\n    <script>kernelName = 'python3'</script>", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["py-modindex", "Python Module Index", "", "modules"], ["overview/overview", "High Level Overview", "N", "next"], ["rh_primitives/table", "Table", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "secrets/secrets.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Secrets Management</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#secrets\">secrets</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": true, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "secrets/secrets", "sidebars": ["sidebar-logo.html", "search-field.html", "sbt-sidebar-nav.html", "sbt-sidebar-footer.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12", "pagetitle": "Secrets Management", "page_description": "Secrets Management  Runhouse provides a convenient interface for managing your secrets in a secure manner. Secrets are stored in Vault, and never on Runhouse se", "author": "the Runhouse team \ud83c\udfc3\u200d\u2640\ufe0f\ud83c\udfe0", "github_user": "run-house", "github_repo": "runhouse", "github_version": "main", "doc_path": "docs/", "theme_search_bar_text": "Search the docs ...", "theme_show_toc_level": 1}